results.name: Zodiak
results.description: Twelve demons merged with Norman Harrison, who, soon after, adopted the guise of Zodiac and used his abilities to harness powers based on the astrological Zodiac.

results.name: Zombie (Simon Garth)
results.description: War hero Simon Garth was turned into a zombie by his secretary, Layla, who was also a voodoo priestess, after being killed by his gardener, Gyps.

results.name: Zuras
results.description: Zuras was once the leader of the Eternals.

results.name: Zzzax
results.description: A chain reaction in an atomic reactor, a result of a terrorist attack, accidentally created a force that absorbed the electrolytes of the nearby humans' brains, granting the explosion of energy a rudimentary sentience.
